pc.name: AZ0_AngelaDeth_PC
pc.biography: <@>A fifteen year veteran of the Desert Rangers, Angie was born into a strict religious community near the southern edge of the Arizona Wastes. When she hit her teens, she rebelled against everything they stood for and in the process, nearly rebelled herself into an early grave. She found the Rangers when she woke up in their drunk tank. Joining them saved her life and she hasn't looked back since.

pc.name: AZ2_VulturesCry_PC
pc.biography: <@>A scout for a Native American tribe from beyond the Arizona waste's southern border, Vulture's Cry has come north to explore and trade, but circumstances have left her stranded far from home.
